Messaging (Event-driven / Async) - asynchronous communication.
    Services lose coupling ( they don't know the other services "state" )
    Ideal to when you don't need a imediate response
Comparison between REST and Messaging


REST 
    Thread pools get exhausted → backpressure problem
    You need:
        Timeouts
        Circuit breakers
        Retries

Messaging 
    Queue acts as natural buffer
    Backpressure handled by:
        Queue size
        Consumer rate